<Layouts.app flash={@flash}>
  <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 mt-5 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <.custom_nav active="chelekom-docs-tabs" />
    <div class="lg:col-span-10">
      <.custom_info
        title="Tabs"
        description="Interactive tab component supporting both horizontal and vertical orientations, designed for Phoenix and Phoenix LiveView, enabling seamless content switching for enhanced user navigation."
        mix="mix mishka.ui.gen.component tabs"
        github="https://github.com/mishka-group/mishka_chelekom/blob/master/priv/components/tabs.eex"
        tags={["Component", "Stateless", "JS-module"]}
      />
      <.custom_tab id="chelekom-tabs-tab">
        <:documentation_panel>
          <.heading2 class="mb-5" id="overview">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/tabs/#overview"}>
              Overview of the Phoenix LiveView Tabs Component
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The
            <strong>
              Mishka Chelekom Tabs
            </strong>
            component is a highly customizable <strong>Phoenix LiveView</strong>
            tool for organizing content in an intuitive tab-based interface. It is ideal for managing multiple sections of information or forms within a single page. This component supports both horizontal and vertical tab layouts, offering a wide range of styling options for colors, sizes, and border styles to match your app's design seamlessly.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_code_wrapper elements_class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <.tabs
              id="sample-1"
              padding="small"
              content_padding="none"
              size="small"
              variant="nav_pills"
              border="extra_small"
              rounded="large"
              color="base"
              gap="small"
              hide_list_border
              full_width_tab
              class="bg-white shadow-lg dark:bg-[#323238] py-5 px-3 rounded-lg border-[#E5E7EB] dark:border-[#454549]"
            >
              <:tab on_select={JS.push("something", value: %{name: "mishka.tools"})}>
                Login
              </:tab>
              <:tab>Sigup</:tab>
              <:panel>
                <div class="space-y-5 mt-5">
                  <div class="bg-[#F4F4F5] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:bg-[#27272A] space-y-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg">
                    <label class="block">Email <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input
                      type="email"
                      class="block w-full p-0 h-6 bg-transparent border-0 appearance-none outline-none focus:outline-none"
                      placeholder="Enter Email"
                      name="email"
                      disabled
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-[#F4F4F5] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:bg-[#27272A] space-y-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg">
                    <label class="block">Password <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input
                      type="password"
                      class="block w-full p-0 h-6 bg-transparent border-0 appearance-none outline-none focus:outline-none"
                      placeholder="Enter Password"
                      name="email"
                      disabled
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-center">
                    Need to create an account?
                    <span class="text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-400">Sign up</span>
                  </div>
                  <.button
                    full_width
                    size="leading-5 py-2 px-4"
                    variant="text-white bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-700"
                    border="none"
                  >
                    Send
                  </.button>
                </div>
              </:panel>
              <:panel>
                <div class="space-y-5 mt-5">
                  <div class="bg-[#F4F4F5] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:bg-[#27272A] space-y-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg">
                    <label class="block">Name <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      class="block w-full p-0 h-6 bg-transparent border-0 appearance-none outline-none focus:outline-none"
                      placeholder="Enter Name"
                      name="email"
                      disabled
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-[#F4F4F5] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:bg-[#27272A] space-y-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg">
                    <label class="block">Email <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input
                      type="email"
                      class="block w-full p-0 h-6 bg-transparent border-0 appearance-none outline-none focus:outline-none"
                      placeholder="Enter Email"
                      name="email"
                      disabled
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-[#F4F4F5] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 dark:bg-[#27272A] space-y-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg">
                    <label class="block">Password <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input
                      type="password"
                      class="block w-full p-0 h-6 bg-transparent border-0 appearance-none outline-none focus:outline-none"
                      placeholder="Enter Password"
                      name="email"
                      disabled
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-center">
                    Already have an account?
                    <span class="text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-400">Login</span>
                  </div>
                  <.button
                    full_width
                    size="leading-5 py-2 px-4"
                    variant="text-white bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-700"
                    border="none"
                  >
                    Send
                  </.button>
                </div>
              </:panel>
            </.tabs>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <.tabs
                id="sample-2"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="danger"
                rounded="full"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>Home</:tab>
                <:tab active>About</:tab>
                <:tab>Contact</:tab>
              </.tabs>
              <.tabs
                id="sample-3"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="primary"
                rounded="small"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>Products</:tab>
                <:tab>Services</:tab>
                <:tab>Support</:tab>
                <:tab>Blog</:tab>
              </.tabs>
              <.tabs
                id="sample-4"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="misc"
                rounded="medium"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>Profile</:tab>
                <:tab>Settings</:tab>
              </.tabs>
              <.tabs
                id="sample-5"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="dawn"
                rounded="large"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>News</:tab>
                <:tab>Events</:tab>
                <:tab>Timeline</:tab>
              </.tabs>
              <.tabs
                id="sample-6"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="base"
                rounded="extra_large"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>Features</:tab>
                <:tab>Documentation</:tab>
                <:tab>Resources</:tab>
              </.tabs>
              <.tabs
                id="sample-7"
                padding="extra_small"
                size="extra_small"
                variant="nav_pills"
                color="secondary"
                rounded="full"
                gap="extra_small"
              >
                <:tab>Login</:tab>
                <:tab>Register</:tab>
                <:tab active>Reset</:tab>
                <:tab>Help</:tab>
                <:tab>Contact</:tab>
              </.tabs>
            </div>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.cp margin="mt-5">
            This
            <strong>
              <.link
                title="Phoenix LiveView component"
                class="transition-colors hover:text-[#448D96]"
                navigate={~p"/chelekom"}
              >
                Phoenix LiveView component
              </.link>
            </strong>
            also offers multiple tab styles, including active, inactive, or disabled states, making it easy to organize and navigate complex content. The flexibility in vertical and horizontal tab layouts ensures a responsive and visually appealing user experience, tailored to different use cases.
          </.cp>

          <.custom_block position="left" color="success" class="my-8" border="medium">
            <.cp>
              By using the class prop, you can apply custom classes or Tailwind CSS classes to customize the appearance and behavior of the components, allowing for flexible design changes.
            </.cp>
          </.custom_block>
          <.custom_block position="left" color="danger" class="my-8" border="medium">
            <strong>NOTICE:</strong> each tab component needs a unique ID
          </.custom_block>

          <.custom_block position="left" color="primary" class="my-8" border="medium">
            <.cp>
              <strong>Server-driven active tab:</strong>
              the
              <.custom_inline_code>active</.custom_inline_code>
              attribute is reactive — it is rendered server-side and updates on every re-render. Bind it to an assign (e.g. <.custom_inline_code>{~s|active={@current_tab == "settings"}|}</.custom_inline_code>) and switch tabs by <.custom_inline_code>push_patch</.custom_inline_code>/<.custom_inline_code>JS.patch</.custom_inline_code> from anywhere on the page; the active tab and panel will follow. The active state is also present in the static HTML on first mount, so it works before LiveView connects (useful for tests, SEO, and JS-disabled clients).
            </.cp>
          </.custom_block>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="base-tabs">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/tabs/#base-tabs"}>
              Base Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.custom_code_wrapper code_class="text-sm" elements_class="space-y-5" code={@code_14}>
            <.tabs id="tab-example-13432" padding="large">
              <:tab icon="hero-user-circle">Profile</:tab>
              <:tab badge="8" badge_size="size-[19px]">Tickets</:tab>
              <:tab icon="hero-cog-6-tooth">Settings</:tab>

              <:panel>
                <.cp>
                  The Profile tab allows you to view and edit your personal details. Keep your information up to date to ensure a seamless experience across the platform.
                </.cp>
              </:panel>
              <:panel>
                <.cp>
                  In the Tickets tab, you can manage all your active and past tickets. Whether you need assistance or just want to check your ticket history, this tab has all the relevant details.
                </.cp>
              </:panel>
              <:panel>
                <.cp>
                  The Settings tab gives you access to customizable options for your account. Here, you can adjust notifications, privacy settings, and other preferences to personalize your experience.
                </.cp>
              </:panel>
            </.tabs>
          </.custom_code_wrapper>

          <.heading2 margin="my-5" id="default-variant-tabs">
            <.link patch={~p"/chelekom/docs/tabs/#default-variant-tabs"}>
              Default Variant
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The <.link navigate={~p"/chelekom/docs/tabs"}>Mishka Chelekom tabs</.link>
            of the Mishka Chelekom Tabs component provides a simple and clean style where only the active tab’s color and border color are changed.
          </.cp>

